data.title: Michael Chang
data.meta_description: Michael Chang during a practice session at the AFAS Tennis Classics in Eindhoven, The Netherlands. UPDATE: On May 25th 2009 this picture was featured in the French online magazine L' Internaute in an article by Jérémy Talbot; the same journalist that had previously used my photo of Goran Ivanisevic in another article.
data.text:
Michael Chang during a practice session at the AFAS Tennis Classics in Eindhoven, The Netherlands.

UPDATE: On May 25th 2009 this picture was featured in the French online magazine L' Internaute in an article by Jérémy Talbot; the same journalist that had previously used my photo of Goran Ivanisevic in another article.
